# Determinism (non-negotiable)

- Workflow code must be replay-safe and deterministic.
- No direct I/O, network, DB, filesystem, random, or real time inside workflows.
- Put side effects in Activities; workflow coordinates and awaits them.

## Allowed patterns

- Use Temporal workflow APIs for time/sleep/timers.
- Keep workflow state explicit; use signals/queries intentionally.
- Keep activities small, idempotent, and well-retried.

## Imports

- Workflow code should avoid Node-only libs and side-effectful modules.
- Shared types are fine; activity implementations can import heavier deps.
